    - [x] Stress tensor.
    - [x] K-paths.
    - [ ] Projections over orbitals...
    - [ ] ...


- [x] Plot module
    - [x] Plotting phonon and electronic spectra
    - [x] Comparing spectrums
    - [ ] ...
